					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This badly damaged inscription refers itself to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Akālavarsha.</hi> Since the date portion is damaged, it is not possible to say to which Akālavarsha it should be assigned. The alphabet is, however, too late for Kṛishṇa I. It seems to record the death of a hero in a cattle-raid.</p>						

						</summary>
